sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as API Service
    participant DDB as DynamoDB
    participant SQS as SQS (printer queue)

    C->>API: POST /jobs/id/release {printerName}
    API->>DDB: UpdateItem(SET status=RELEASED WHERE status=HELD)
    alt Condition succeeds
        DDB-->>API: 200 OK
        API->>SQS: SendMessage({jobId, s3Key})
        SQS-->>API: 200 OK
        API-->>C: 200 {status: RELEASED}
    else Already released / not HELD
        DDB-->>API: ConditionalCheckFailedException
        API-->>C: 409 Conflict
    end
